  "field_acl_comment": "Optional read-path field ACL. Per instance (use 'default' for the default instance), per model, exactly one of 'deny' (blacklist) or 'allow' (exclusive whitelist). '*' is a per-instance model wildcard. Denied fields are removed from every read tool, resource, and knowledge index, with a redacted_fields note; aggregation on a denied field is rejected. No field_acl key = no change. See docs/field-acl.md.",
